---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — River Primavera Wijaya" activePage="about">
<div class="main-wrap">

  <div class="about-layout">
    <div class="about-top">
      <img src="/assets/photo.jpg.png" alt="River Wijaya" class="about-photo"
           onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
      <div>
        <h1 class="about-name">River Primavera Wijaya</h1>
        <p class="about-role">Management Consultant · Builder · Learner</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-body">
      <p>Hi, I'm River, a marketer at heart who believes in the power of a good story. But as I've been drawn into tech, software and engineering, I've found myself wanting to build things that are both functional and meaningful.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section-title">Experience</div>
    <div class="about-exp">
      <div class="about-exp-item">
        <img src="/assets/accenture-logo.png" alt="Accenture" class="about-exp-logo"
             onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
        <div>
          <div class="about-exp-role">Management Consultant Analyst</div>
          <div class="about-exp-company">Accenture · May 2026 – Present</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-exp-item">
        <img src="/assets/mganik-group.png" alt="mGanik" class="about-exp-logo"
             onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
        <div>
          <div class="about-exp-role">Project Executive (Internship)</div>
          <div class="about-exp-company">mGanik · Sep 2025 – Feb 2026</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section-title">Connect</div>
    <div class="about-links">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/river-wijaya" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-link">
        <span class="about-link-icon">in</span>
        <div><div class="about-link-name">LinkedIn</div><div class="about-link-sub">River Wijaya</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/Onchch" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-link">
        <span class="about-link-icon">gh</span>
        <div><div class="about-link-name">GitHub</div><div class="about-link-sub">Onchch</div></div>
      </a>
      <a href="mailto:rivwij@gmail.com" class="about-link">
        <span class="about-link-icon">@</span>
        <div><div class="about-link-name">Email</div><div class="about-link-sub">rivwij@gmail.com</div></div>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
<footer><span>River Primavera Wijaya</span><span>Jakarta · Always learning</span></footer>
</BaseLayout>
